    <item>
      <title>随着市场重新开放，日本股市面临日元波动性飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japanese-stocks-face-surge-in-yen-volatility-as-market-reopens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市将于假期后重新开市，这让交易者首次有机会对周一日元汇率的波动做出反应，日元汇率波动引发了人们对日本政府干预支持日元汇率的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japanese-stocks-face-surge-in-yen-volatility-as-market-reopens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 22:31:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国央行希望停止而不是加入债券购买热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-central-bank-wants-to-halt-bond-buying-spree-not-join-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场充斥着有关央行即将开始购买政府债券的传言。中国人民银行本身正在努力解决一个不同的问题：太多人似乎渴望购买它们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-central-bank-wants-to-halt-bond-buying-spree-not-join-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的 PacifiCorp 现在面临 300 亿美元的火灾索赔要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 旗下的 PacifiCorp 目前面临 2020 年俄勒冈州劳动节野火受害者索要 300 亿美元的索赔，这是对美国西部最大电网运营商的法律攻击升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:54:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙的巴克什更换了三名高级管理人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-29/paramount-s-bakish-replaced-with-three-senior-executives-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 取代了首席执行官鲍勃·巴基什 (Bob Bakish)，并任命了一个管理委员会，董事会正在就公司控制权可能发生的变更进行谈判。派拉蒙公司的三位最高级管理人员；布莱恩·罗宾斯 (Brian Robbins)、克里斯·麦卡锡 (Chris McCarthy) 和乔治·奇克斯 (George Cheeks) 将负责运营该公司。吉萨·兰加纳坦 (Getha Ranganathan) 还有更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-29/paramount-s-bakish-replaced-with-three-senior-executives-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷选择摩根大通和摩根士丹利进行 IPO 或出售 StandardAero</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/carlyle-is-said-to-pick-banks-for-ipo-or-sale-of-standardaero</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正在与摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase) 合作。据知情人士透露，公司和摩根士丹利正在讨论飞机维修服务提供商 StandardAero 的选择权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/carlyle-is-said-to-pick-banks-for-ipo-or-sale-of-standardaero</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 20:46:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧舒丹董事长以 60 亿欧元估值发起收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/billionaire-launches-l-occitane-buyout-at-6-4-billion-valuation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧舒丹国际公司（L’Occitane International SA）的亿万富翁老板雷诺德·盖格（Reinold Geiger）希望将这家护肤品公司私有化，此举可能会结束该公司在香港证券交易所 14 年的上市历程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/billionaire-launches-l-occitane-buyout-at-6-4-billion-valuation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 15:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司发行 100 亿美元债券获得喘息机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/boeing-looks-to-sell-bonds-after-reporting-cash-burn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司周一通过债券发行筹集了 100 亿美元资金，吸引了约 770 亿美元的订单，并允许该飞机制造商通过为其巨额债务负担的部分再融资来缓解部分财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/boeing-looks-to-sell-bonds-after-reporting-cash-burn</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 12:33:16 GMT</pubDate>
